Package: HW3
Type: Package
Title: What the Package Does (Title Case)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Edward Shao
Maintainer: Edward Shao <eshao@umich.edu>
Description: 
    ‘HW3’ package is created for the purpose of copying the lm() and anova() functions, 
    which can give us the fitted linear regression model and the results of hypothesis testing: 
    ‘lm2()’ fits the linear regression model based on given formula and data, and returns the values similar to ones given from the ‘summary()’ 
    ‘anova2()’ performs analysis of varaince on the fitted linear regression model for the purpose of hypothesis testing.
